gender runner Nikki Hiltz is headed to the Paris Olympics,\\\"NBC Newsdeclared.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 521, \"end\": 532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transgender\", \"score\": 0.9999999995407052, \"rank\": 4.59145509470712e-10, \"text\": \"Transgender\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transgender\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transgender\"}, {\"begin\": 540, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikki_Hiltz\", \"score\": 0.9999994965743456, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nikki Hiltz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikki_Hiltz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikki_Hiltz\"}, {\"begin\": 569, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Transgender runner Nikki Hiltz punched their ticket to Paris after winning the 1500 meter race at Sunday's U.S. Track and Field Olympic Trials.https://t.co/WMqyVga1fR  - NBC News (@NBCNews)July 2, 2024    After the qualifier, Hiltz talked about how glad she was to have garnered the achievement on the final day of LGBT \\\"pride\\\" month.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 604, \"end\": 615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transgender\", \"score\": 0.9999999995407052, \"rank\": 4.59145509470712e-10, \"text\": \"Transgender\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transgender\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transgender\"}, {\"begin\": 623, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikki_Hiltz\", \"score\": 0.9999994965743456, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nikki Hiltz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q